== English ==
=== Adjective ===
[[Category:English adjectives]]
'''simplistic'''
# In a manner that [[simplifies]] the issue to a degree where many important details are lost
#:'''usage note:''' This is not to be conflated with [[simple]].  '''simplistic''' implies simplicity to excess, whereas [[simple]] does not.
